M|Pitf|**Sy|** "rv growing 50%!" (ignoring burn, churn, unit economics)
M|Pitf|**Co|** Unsustainable growth. Scaling broken md.
M|Pitf|fix|** Look at all four dimensions together.
M|Pitf|tx|---
M|Pitf|**Sy|** "We're not profitable yet, is that bad?" (early-stage company)
M|Pitf|**Co|** Misplaced worry. Early-stage shd op for growth and unit economics, not profitability.
M|Pitf|fix|** Use stage-appropriate benchmarks.
M|Pitf|tx|---
M|Pitf|**Sy|** "Churn is 5%, let's watch it"
M|Pitf|**Co|** By the time lagging indicators (churn, NRR) show problems, it's late.
M|Pitf|fix|** Track leading indicators (usage, engagement, onboarding completion).
M|Pitf|tx|---
M|Pitf|**Sy|** "NRR <100% for 3 quarters, but we'll fix it eventually"
